Class DataSourceContainer

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.tools.visualvm.core.datasource.DataSourceProvider
      com.sun.tools.visualvm.core.datasource.DataSourceContainer

public final class DataSourceContainer
extends DataSourceProvider

Default implementation of DataSourceContainer. This class implements all neccessary methods to act as a repository of a DataSource (DataSource.getRepository()).

Author:
Jiri Sedlacek
